### STEP 3: Redesign AnalysisResults Component

**File to modify:** `/Users/user/Desktop/K3rn.labas_test/k3rn-platform/src/components/capture/analysis-results.tsx`

This is the largest change. The component must be refactored from displaying the old format to displaying the canonical output.

